\par \pard \qc \li1200\ri1200 \sb0 \fi0 BRIEF AMICI CURIAE OF THE NATIONAL BAR ASSOCIATION AND THE COUNCIL OF 100-AN ORGANIZATION OF BLACK REPUBLICANS, INC. IN SUPPORT OF RESPONDENTS
