\par \b \i0 \ul0 \pard \ql \li0\ri0 \sb0 \fi0 COUNSEL: \b0 \i0 \ul0 J. CLAY SMITH, JR., * HOWARD UNIVERSITY, SCHOOL OF LAW, 2900 Van Ness Street, N.W., Washington, D.C. 20008, 202 806-8028 
